::Kaiser::
       "I'm on my way."  He closes the channel and walks groggily to the 
tactical display room.  He has to shake his head several times along the way 
just to stay focused.  Upon his arrival he nods at Tyrael.  "Major."  He then 
takes his customary seat next to the commander.

--part1_1f0.4dc7385.2babf7f7_boundary
